F = Medicaid Agency
G = Grocery
H = Home Health Care / IV Infusion 
I = Inpatient Hospital 
K = Clinic
L = Long Term Care (nursing home)
M = Mail Order Pharmacy
N = Null - unique in house use 
O = Unknown type of service 
P = Private/HMO Pharmacy 
Q = DME-Durable Medical  
       Equipment
R = Retail Pharmacy
S = Sovereign/ ITU -Native American 
W = Internet

