      BEGIN DSSUBRECORD
         Name "PDX_TYP"
         Description =+=+=+=
ESI assigned values are:
A = Armed Forces 
B = Injectable/Specialty Meds
C = Clearinghouse
D = Doctor
E = Excl. from Directoryâ\(20AC)\(201C)Closed door
F = Medicaid Agency
G = Grocery
H = Home Health Care / IV Infusion 
I = Inpatient Hospital 
K = Clinic
L = Long Term Care (nursing home)
M = Mail Order Pharmacy
N = Null - unique in house use 
O = Unknown type of service 
P = Private/HMO Pharmacy 
Q = DME-Durable Medical  
       Equipment
R = Retail Pharmacy
S = Sovereign/ ITU -Native American 
W = Internet

=+=+=+=
         SqlType "1"
         Precision "1"
         Scale "0"
         Nullable "0"
         KeyPosition "0"
         DisplaySize "0"
