ins the SQL statement to run once on each node before any data is processed on that node.\" engines=\"ee\" label=\"Before SQL (node)\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" multiline=\"true\" name=\"beforeNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Select Yes to read the SQL statement from the file that is specified in the Before SQL (node) statement property.\" label=\"Read Before SQL (node) statement from file\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"ReadFromFileBeforeSQLNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"true\" description=\"Abort the job if there is an error executing a command\" label=\"Fail on error\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"FailOnError\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/></Property><Property default=\"\" description=\"Enter the SQL statement or the fully-qualified name of the file that contains the SQL statement to run once one each node after all data is processed on that node.\" engines=\"ee\" label=\"After SQL (node)\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" multiline=\"true\" name=\"afterNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"string\"><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Select Yes to read the SQL statement from the file that is specified in the After SQL (node) statement property.\" label=\"Read After SQL (node) statement from file\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"ReadFromFileAfterSQLNode\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/><Property default=\"true\" description=\"Abort the job if there is an error executing a command\" label=\"Fail on error\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"0\" name=\"FailOnError\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"/></Property></Property><Property contexts=\"target\" default=\"0\" deprecated=\"false\" description=\"Determines how records should be ordered across multiple links.\" engines=\"ee\" filterContexts=\"all\" filterEngines=\"all\" hidden=\"false\" inputLinkCountConstraint=\"multiple\" label=\"Record ordering\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" multiline=\"false\"