tList\" calloutDescription=\"Lists the detected databases. The value for the Instance property does not affect the databases that are detected. The list includes only the databases for the currently configured, active DB2 instance in the DB2 Connector environment.\" calloutLabel=\"Database\" calloutType=\"enumerator\" description=\"Specifies the name of the database/location to connect to.\" label=\"Database/Location\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"Database\" required=\"true\" type=\"string\" xsi:type=\"asc:CalloutProperty\"><CalloutArgument name=\"class\">Databases</CalloutArgument></Property><Property description=\"Specifies the user name to use for connecting to the database.\" label=\"User name\" maxLength=\"256\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minLength=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"Username\" required=\"false\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"string\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the password to use for connecting to the database.\" label=\"Password\" maxLength=\"256\" maxOccurs=\"1\" minLength=\"1\" minOccurs=\"1\" name=\"Password\" required=\"false\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"protectedstring\"/><Property description=\"Specifies the full path to the DB2 client library file. If not specified, the system default library name for the currently configured DB2 environment is used.\" label=\"DB2 client library file\" maxLength=\"256\" minLength=\"1\" name=\"DB2ClientLibFile\" required=\"false\" transactionModels=\"local\" type=\"string\"/><Property default=\"false\" description=\"Select this option if you want to provide alternate connection settings to use on the conductor node. The stage is configured to run in parallel mode.\" engines=\"ee\" filterChildPropertiesOnValue=\"true\" label=\"Alternate conductor settings\" name=\"Conductor\" required=\"false\" type=\"bool\"><Property description=\"Specifies the name of the instance to use as active instance for running parallel jobs and on the conductor node. If not specified, the value of the DB2INSTANCE